      "title": "Tenant event flow",
      "description": "Per-tenant lifecycle outcomes from auditflow_tenant_events_total: routed = pipeline set ran to completion, delivered = a pipeline delivered to its sink, quarantined = no routable set (unprovisioned/disabled in-flight).",
